{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775865834218,"sessionID":"ses_28627d2a7ffecz2E2EsusqJaAu","part":{"id":"prt_d79d98b8e001OnKHqlnDQVP5FR","messageID":"msg_d79d97f6b001n9uP0nwF02AqMM","sessionID":"ses_28627d2a7ffecz2E2EsusqJaAu","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_965bd20bd0ff4bbd87a95095","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型增强\n\n## Summary\n\n增强 MetadataService 和数据模型，实现完整的元数据生命周期管理和验证功能。\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\n`AgentMetadata` 和 `MetadataService` 是 CLI 核心的元数据管理组件。当前实现存在以下问题:\n1. `AgentMetadata` 位于 `services` 包，而非 `models` 包\n2. 缺少 `update_metadata` 方法\n3. 缺少语言特定的工作区验证\n4. `MetadataOptions` 缺少 `from_options` 类方法\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 迁移 AgentMetadata 到 models 包统一管理\n2. 实现完整的 MetadataService CRUD 操作\n3. 添加语言特定验证逻辑\n4. 增强 MetadataOptions\n\n### Value\n\n- **模块化**: 数据模型与业务逻辑分离\n- **可维护性**: 统一的模型定义位置\n- **完整性**: 完整的元数据生命周期支持\n- **可验证性**: 语言特定工作区验证\n\n---\n\n## Scope\n\n### In-Scope\n\n| Component | Path | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| AgentMetadata | `agentcube/models/agent_models.py` | 新的独立模型文件 |\n| MetadataOptions | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | 增强的方法 |\n| MetadataService | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 新增方法 |\n| Unit tests | `tests/test_metadata_service.py` | 测试覆盖 |\n\n### Out-of-Scope\n\n- CLI 命令参数变更\n- Runtime 类修改\n- 数据库持久化\n\n---\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose | Status |\n|------------|---------|--------|\n| `pydantic>=2.0.0` | 数据模型验证 | Existing |\n| `pyyaml>=6.0` | YAML 序列化 | Existing |\n\n### Upstream\n\n- `cli-toolkit/design.md` — MetadataService 设计\n- `cli-toolkit/spec.md` — 元数据需求\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n1. **PackRuntime** — 元数据加载和验证\n2. **BuildRuntime** — 版本管理\n3. **PublishRuntime** — 部署信息\n4. **InvokeRuntime** — 端点信息\n\n### Risks\n\n| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |\n|------|----------|------------|\n| Import 变更 | Medium | 保持向后兼容导出 |\n| 破坏性变更 | High | 添加兼容层 |\n\n---\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Option 1: 保持现状 (Not Selected)\n\n仅添加缺失方法，不移动模型位置。\n\n**Cons**:\n- 模型定义位置不合理\n- 不符合设计 spec\n\n### Option 2: 完全重构 (Selected)\n\n迁移 AgentMetadata 到 models 包，增强 MetadataService。\n\n**Pros**:\n- 符合设计规范\n- 模块化更好\n- 便于维护\n\n**Cons**:\n- 需要更新多个 import\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: 模型迁移\n- [ ] 创建 `agentcube/models/agent_models.py`\n- [ ] 移动 AgentMetadata 到新文件\n- [ ] 更新 models/__init__.py 导出\n- [ ] 更新 services/metadata_service.py import\n\n### Phase 2: MetadataService 增强\n- [ ] 实现 `update_metadata` 方法\n- [ ] 实现 `_validate_python_workspace` 方法\n- [ ] 实现 `_validate_java_workspace` 方法\n- [ ] 更新 save_metadata 使用 exclude_none\n\n### Phase 3: MetadataOptions 增强\n- [ ] 添加 `from_options` 类方法\n- [ ] 确保字段默认值一致\n\n### Phase 4: 测试\n- [ ] 更新现有测试 import\n- [ ] 添加新方法测试\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n### AgentMetadata 模型\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| AM-001 | 导出路径 | `from agentcube.models import AgentMetadata` 可用 |\n| AM-002 | 字段验证 | language 只能是 python/java |\n| AM-003 | 字段验证 | port 范围 1-65535 |\n| AM-004 | 默认值 | language 默认为 python |\n\n### MetadataService\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| MS-001 | load_metadata | 正确加载 agent_metadata.yaml |\n| MS-002 | save_metadata | 使用 exclude_none=True |\n| MS-003 | update_metadata | 正确合并更新并保存 |\n| MS-004 | validate_python | 无 .py 文件时抛出 ValueError |\n| MS-005 | validate_java | 无 pom.xml 时抛出 ValueError |\n\n### MetadataOptions\n\n| ID | Scenario | Expected Result |\n|----|----------|-----------------|\n| MO-001 | from_options | 正确从 dict 创建实例 |\n\n---\n\n## Technical Design\n\n### AgentMetadata 模型\n\n```python\n# agentcube/models/agent_models.py\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel, Field, field_validator\nfrom typing import Optional, Dict, Any\n\nclass AgentMetadata(BaseModel):\n    model_config = {\"extra\": \"forbid\"}\n    \n    agent_name: str = Field(..., description=\"Unique name identifying the agent\")\n    description: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\"Human-readable summary\")\n    language: str = Field(default=\"python\", description=\"Programming language used\")\n    entrypoint: str = Field(..., description=\"Command to launch the agent\")\n    port: int = Field(default=8080, description=\"Port exposed by the agent runtime\")\n    build_mode: str = Field(default=\"local\", description=\"Build strategy: local or cloud\")\n    region: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\"Deployment region\")\n    version: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\"Semantic version string\")\n    image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None)\n    auth: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None)\n    requirements_file: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"requirements.txt\")\n    registry_url: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"\")\n    registry_username: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"\")\n    registry_password: Optional[str] = Field(default=\"\")\n    agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n    workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n    router_url: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n    readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n    readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = Field(default=None)\n    agent_id: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n    session_id: Optional[str] = Field(default=None)\n    k8s_deployment: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None)\n\n    @field_validator(\"language\")\n    @classmethod\n    def validate_language(cls, v: str) -> str:\n        v_lower = v.lower()\n        if v_lower not in (\"python\", \"java\"):\n            raise ValueError(\"Language must be 'python' or 'java'\")\n        return v_lower\n\n    @field_validator(\"build_mode\")\n    @classmethod\n    def validate_build_mode(cls, v: str) -> str:\n        v_lower = v.lower()\n        if v_lower not in (\"local\", \"cloud\"):\n            raise ValueError(\"Build mode must be 'local' or 'cloud'\")\n        return v_lower\n\n    @field_validator(\"port\")\n    @classmethod\n    def validate_port(cls, v: int) -> int:\n        if not isinstance(v, int):\n            raise ValueError(\"Port must be an integer\")\n        if v < 1 or v > 65535:\n            raise ValueError(\"Port must be between 1 and 65535\")\n        return v\n```\n\n### MetadataService 更新\n\n```python\n# agentcube/services/metadata_service.py\nfrom agentcube.models.agent_models import AgentMetadata\n\nclass MetadataService:\n    METADATA_FILES = [\"agent_metadata.yaml\", \"agent.yaml\", \"metadata.yaml\"]\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def load_metadata(workspace_path: str | Path) -> AgentMetadata: ...\n    \n    @staticmethod\n    def save_metadata(workspace_path: str | Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Path:\n        workspace = Path(workspace_path)\n        metadata_file = workspace / \"agent_metadata.yaml\"\n        \n        with open(metadata_file, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n            yaml.safe_dump(\n                metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True), \n                f, \n                default_flow_style=False, \n                sort_keys=False\n            )\n        return metadata_file\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def update_metadata(workspace_path: str | Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n        \"\"\"Load, merge updates, save pattern.\"\"\"\n        metadata = MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n        updated = metadata.model_copy(update=updates)\n        MetadataService.save_metadata(workspace_path, updated)\n        return updated\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def validate_workspace(workspace_path: str | Path) -> bool: ...\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def _validate_python_workspace(workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n        py_files = list(workspace_path.glob(\"*.py\"))\n        if not py_files:\n            raise ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def _validate_java_workspace(workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n        pom_file = workspace_path / \"pom.xml\"\n        if not pom_file.exists():\n            raise ValueError(\"No pom.xml found in workspace\")\n```\n\n### MetadataOptions 增强\n\n```python\n# agentcube/models/pack_models.py\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import Optional, Dict, Any\n\n@dataclass\nclass MetadataOptions:\n    agent_name: Optional[str] = None\n    language: Optional[str] = \"python\"\n    entrypoint: Optional[str] = None\n    port: Optional[int] = 8080\n    build_mode: Optional[str] = \"local\"\n    description: Optional[str] = None\n    requirements_file: Optional[str] = None\n    output: Optional[str] = None\n    verbose: bool = False\n    workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    router_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = 8080\n    registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = \"\"\n\n    @classmethod\n    def from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"MetadataOptions\":\n        \"\"\"Create MetadataOptions from CLI options dictionary.\"\"\"\n        valid_fields = {f.name for f in cls.__dataclass_fields__.values()}\n        filtered = {k: v for k, v in options.items() if k in valid_fields}\n        return cls(**filtered)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Timeline Estimate\n\n| Phase | Effort |\n|-------|--------|\n| 模型迁移 | 1-2 hours |\n| MetadataService 增强 | 2 hours |\n| MetadataOptions 增强 | 1 hour |\n| 测试 | 2 hours |\n| **Total** | **6-7 hours** |\n\n---\n\n## Existing Implementation Status\n\n当前实现位于:\n- `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` (139 lines) — AgentMetadata + MetadataService\n- `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` (27 lines) — MetadataOptions\n\n### Current Gaps\n\n1. **模型位置**: AgentMetadata 在 services 包而非 models 包\n2. **缺少 update_metadata**: 设计中要求但未实现\n3. **缺少验证方法**: _validate_python_workspace, _validate_java_workspace 未实现\n4. **MetadataOptions**: 缺少 from_options 类方法\n5. **save_metadata**: 未使用 exclude_none=True","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/models/pack_models.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/models/__init__.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tests/test_metadata_service.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775865834126,"end":1775865834214}}}}
